    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six. This example features a recently serviced VANOS system and reinforced rear subframe mounting points to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a functional M-variable limited-slip differential. Performance is enhanced by a set of Bilstein coilovers, providing superior damping and reduced unsprung weight. While the exterior displays minor wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the engine pull is linear and the valvetrain is exceptionally quiet. A turn-key enthusiast machine for those prioritizing mechanical excellence over concours perfection.",
